metadata.dc:description: 32 cases of cancer of the mobile portion of the tongue are studied. Comments are made about its aetiology, diagnosis and results of different treatment techniques.
metadata.dc:title: Cáncer de la porción móvil de la lengua: estudio de revisión.
[Cancer of the mobile portion of the tongue: a review study].
